    "post_content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>smestreet.in<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Confederation of Women Entrepreneurs (COWE), is hosting the prestigious The Women’s International Summit on Entrepreneurship (WISE) &amp; B2B Expo 2025, on February 28th and March 1st, 2025, at the Engineering Staff College in Gachibowli, Hyderabad, India. WISE is a transformative event empowering women entrepreneurs by providing a platform for networking, learning, and collaboration. This premier event will bring together industry leaders, policymakers, global trade representatives, and women entrepreneurs. The goal is to foster cross-sector collaborations, technological innovations, and sustainable business growth. This prestigious event, funded under the International Cooperation Scheme of the Ministry of Micro, Small &amp; Medium Enterprises (MSME), Government of India, will highlight the critical role women entrepreneurs play in driving India’s economy. Women-led enterprises contribute significantly, representing 20% of <a href=\"https:\/\/smestreet.in\/search?title=MSMEs\">MSMEs<\/a>, employing over 23% of the workforce, and accounting for nearly 13.5 to 15% of the GDP. <a href=\"https:\/\/smestreet.in\/sectors\/cowe-hosts-wise-2025-for-women-entrepreneurs-in-hyderabad-8753881\">Read more<\/a><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->",
