    "post_content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>thekashmirhorizon.com<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In a significant step towards empowering rural entrepreneurs, the Jammu and Kashmir Rural Livelihoods Mission (JKRLM) signed a Memorandum of Understanding (MoU) with the Confederation of Indian Industry (CII) on Wednesday to empower rural entrepreneurs through Industry Led Mentorship program. The MoU was signed by Mission Director, JKRLM, Indu Kanwal Chib and representatives from CII in presence of Secretary, Rural Development Department and Panchayati Raj, Dr. Shahid Iqbal Choudhary. Addressing the gathering, Secretary RDD commended the JKRLM team for their self-motivation and inspiring work they have been doing. He expressed gratitude to the Mission Director, JKRLM and her entire team for their efforts and assured them of the department’s support in capacity building and other areas. <a href=\"https:\/\/thekashmirhorizon.com\/2024\/06\/13\/jkrlm-inks-mou-with-cii-to-empower-rural-entrepreneurs-through-industry-mentorship\/\">Read More<\/a><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->",
