    "post_content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>timesofindia.indiatimes.com<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Addressing the G20 Ministerial Conference on Women’s Empowerment in Gandhinagar, Gujarat on August 2, 2023, PM Narendra Modi underscored the critical role played by women in fostering inclusivity and driving positive change. Pointing out that when women prosper, the world prospers, the Prime Minister underlined that economic empowerment of women fuels growth, and their access to education drives global progress. Their leadership fosters inclusivity, and their voices inspire positive change, he added. He underlined that the most effective way to empower women is through a women-led development approach, pointing out that India was making huge strides in this direction. <a href=\"https:\/\/timesofindia.indiatimes.com\/blogs\/truth-lies-and-politics\/empowering-women-for-global-progress-pms-message-at-g20-conference-on-womens-empowerment\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Read More<\/a><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->",
