    "post_content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>nktv.in<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>FICCI Ladies Organisation (FLO), Northeast Chapter is organising the 5th Edition of Flo Bazaar on 23 rd and 24 th of September 2022. This two-day event is being held at Nedfi House, G.S. Road, Guwahati from 11:00 AM to 8:00 PM. Flo Bazaar is one of the finest presentations by women entrepreneurs across the Northeast and India. It is expected to enhance the pathways created by FLO Northeast to truly empower women in their businesses leading to Atmanirbharta – Self-dependence. A total of 56 women entrepreneurs from all over the country are participating in this robust Bazaar to showcase their products and services. It is a celebration of Shakti – strengthening her attitude, knowledge, talent and image.  <a href=\"https:\/\/www.nktv.in\/ficci-flo-organises-flo-bazaar\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Read More<\/a><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->",
