    "post_content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>news18.com<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"1\">'Mahila E-Haat' is an online platform from the Women and Child Development Ministry, where women entrepreneurs can sell their products directly and without having to bear any cost. Women and Child Development Minister Maneka Gandhi said \"It is generally not possible for rural women to go to far-off places to sell products made by them. Therefore, we decided to help them in selling their products. The product can include clothing, organic products or toys. The website is completely new and is being done for the first time by any ministry\". The entire business of e-haat can be handled through a mobile and no commission will be taken from the seller or buyer. The website also provides for customised orders. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.news18.com\/news\/india\/centre-launches-e-haat-to-promote-women-entrepreneurs-1213183.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Read More<\/a><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->",
