    "post_date": "2020-12-28 19:16:46",
    "post_date_gmt": "2020-12-28 13:46:46",
    "post_content": "<h4 id=\"women-are-the-largest-untapped-reservoir-of-talent-in-the-world\"><strong>“Women are the largest untapped reservoir of talent in the world”<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p><strong>Sheatwork <\/strong>has tied up with <strong>The Entrepreneurship School<\/strong> to develop <strong>AatmaNirbhar She Agile Startup Program <\/strong>for women who aspire to build and launch their own startup. The program aims to harness your energy in kick starting your dream venture with full pace.<\/p>\n<p><strong>WHO IS THIS PROGRAM FOR?<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>AatmaNirbhar She <\/strong>is structurized for ambitious and innovative women entrepreneurs to enable them to transform their ideas into a business venture.<\/p>\n<p>The program is specifically designed to help current and aspiring women entrepreneurs to identify viable business opportunities and to develop feasible and sustainable plans.<\/p>\n<p><strong>WHAT DO YOU GET?<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Our program focuses on the enhancement of the entrepreneurial and managerial skills of women leading early and ideation stage ventures, thereby honing their skills in the art of building a successful venture step by step with top speed, while mitigating risks.<\/p>\n<p>In eight weeks flat, <strong>AatmaNirbhar She <\/strong>program will take you through the journey of building your startup, part by part alongside continuously improving the business with the help of real-time customer feedback. You will also learn lessons on structuring the business, shrugging off the hesitations of making things, breaking things and selling things. The program ends with a capstone investor pitch.<\/p>\n<p>Our expert faculty and mentors will teach you the art of making products and services that the customers desire. This program will help you develop an entrepreneurial mindset, which is the most essential aspect of a startup journey.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"program-structure\">Program Structure<\/h3>\n<p>The program is conducted through <strong>eight-week online training<\/strong> course offered on the online learning platform.<\/p>\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.entrepreneurship.edu.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/Ideathon_Black.jpg\" alt=\"\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><strong>Ideathon<\/strong><br>1. Entrepreneur’s Mindset<br>2. Idea Generation<br>3. Evaluating an idea<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<!-- \/wp:image --><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.entrepreneurship.edu.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/Product-Market-Fit_Black.jpg\" alt=\"\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><strong>Product Market Fit<br><\/strong>4. Core value Proposition<br>5. Design the Prototype<br>6. Know your customer and competition<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<!-- \/wp:image --><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.entrepreneurship.edu.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/Business-Design_Black-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><strong>Business Design<br><\/strong>7. Define Business Model<br>8. Legal Structure of a Business<br>9. Build the Supply Chain and Distribution Model<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<!-- \/wp:image --><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:column --><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.entrepreneurship.edu.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/Marketing-and-Sales_Black.jpg\" alt=\"\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><strong>Marketing and Sales<\/strong><br>10. Pricing and Packaging<br>11. Selling Skills for a Startup<br>12. Digital Marketing Hack<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<!-- \/wp:image --><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.entrepreneurship.edu.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/Startup-Team-and-Finance_Black.jpg\" alt=\"\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><strong>Startup Team and Finance<\/strong><br>13. Build the Startup team<br>14. Financial Model of a startup<br>15. Frugality<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<!-- \/wp:image --><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.entrepreneurship.edu.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/Demo-Week_Black-1.jpg\" alt=\"\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><strong>Demo Week and Launch<\/strong><br>16. Product Development<br>17. Launching Steps for a startup<br>18. Investment Pitch<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<!-- \/wp:image --><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:column --><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Standard Program Fee : INR 12,000\/- *<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-enquire-now\">Enquire Now !<\/h2>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-submit-your-details-below\">SUBMIT your details below:<\/h2>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:shortcode -->\n[contact-form-7 id=\"14306\" title=\"Contact form 1\"]\n<!-- \/wp:shortcode -->",
