    "post_date_gmt": "2020-10-26 11:05:52",
    "post_content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><em>Women led start up venture, <\/em><\/strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"http:\/\/myjen.ai\/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>myjen.ai<\/em><\/strong><\/a><strong><em> is<\/em><\/strong> creating waves in the new normal. It is a fast growing AI powered communication skills coaching company driven by data sciences and cloud computing. <strong>myjen<\/strong> products use NLP, sentiment analysis and data learning, to give the user personalized and contextual feed.  With corporate offices in India and United States, the company has worked with 50 plus corporate clients and 100,000 trainees in 24 countries. Gauging that the global AI training dataset market size had valued USD 956.5 million in 2019 itself and is expected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 22.5%, myjen.ai leveraged the opportunity and announced thelaunch of its AI based Learning &amp; Development products. Out of the three AI based products designed and created by the startup, <strong>kWurd<\/strong>, an email writing AI coach application and <strong>uSpeek<\/strong>, an AI based tool to improve verbal communication skills, are available in the market presently. Success in any field, is to a large extent determined by your communication skills - and with these new products, myjen.ai is all out to hone them!<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->",
