    "post_content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>www.financialexpress.com 13 May, 2020<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Economic package 2.0 will bring immediate relief for MSME and migrant workers<\/strong> <\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>This\neconomic package is for our cottage industry, home industry, our small-scale\nindustry, our MSME : PM Modi<\/strong><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Definitions of MSMEs changed and investment revised\nupwards<\/strong><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Classification -\nManufacturing and Servies<\/li><li>Micro - investment\nless than Rs 1 crore and turnover less than Rs 5 crore<\/li><li>Small - Investment\nless than Rs 10 crore and turnover of less than Rs 50 crore<\/li><li>Medium - Investment\nless than Rs 20 crore and turnover less than Rs 100 crore<\/li><\/ul>\n<!-- \/wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Collateral free loans for MSMEs announced by the\nFinance Minister<\/strong><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Collateral-free automatic loan to be up to Rs 3 lakh crore will be given out to the MSMEs with a time frame of 4 years with 12 moratorium. 45 lakh MSMEs are to benefit from this scheme. Eligible must have turnover of Rs 100 crore.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Read more at: <a href=\"https:\/\/bit.ly\/3ctYkZL\">https:\/\/bit.ly\/3ctYkZL<\/a><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->",
