    "ID": "15016",
    "post_author": "10",
    "post_date": "2020-05-06 16:44:10",
    "post_date_gmt": "2020-05-06 11:14:10",
    "post_content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>YourStory, April 30, 2020<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Assisting&nbsp; organisations and individuals and helping them reach their full potential, are Kritika V Singh and Lakshmi&nbsp;Ramaswamy. They&nbsp;address this issue through their Bengaluru-based startup Being You! Consulting.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Currently, they operate on B2B and B2C models. To elaborate, the startup offers a multi-pronged approach - ranging from Neuro Linguistic Programming (NLP) to regression method, and inner child healing, among others, to serve individuals as well as corporate entities in a wide variety of areas of coaching, facilitating, nurturing, and healing.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>They use a group coaching format in a corporate setup, which starts with getting to know the participants before their programme. At an individual level, they guide clients to achieve the &nbsp;goals set. Unlike a role of a psychiatrist, they explain that their method involves – giving advice to people so that they can explore options to reach their goals, inform them about the benefits, and the challenges.&nbsp; “In short, we play the devil's advocate to empower them to be confidently make the right choices.”<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Working for the social good definitely, but Kritika and Lakshmi, it is purely a passion project - where the top priority is not money! <\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bit.ly\/2SB44sL\">https:\/\/bit.ly\/2SB44sL<\/a><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->",
